{"word":"καταφρόνησις","slug":"καταφρόνησις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>καταφρόνησις</b></el> <el>(καταφρόνησις, εως) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:καταφρονέω'><el>καταφρονέω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>contempt, disdain</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>without any bad sense, <a href='S:opposed to'>opp. to</a> <el>αὔχημα</el>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}